# Debian XFCE – Complete Removal of IBus (Switch to fcitx5)

This document describes how to **completely remove IBus** from a  
**Debian + XFCE** system and switch to a **single, stable input method: fcitx5**.

> ⚠️ On XFCE, running **IBus and fcitx together causes input conflicts**.  
> For stability, **only one input method should be used**.

---

## 1. Stop Running IBus Processes

```bash
ibus exit || true
pkill ibus || true
2. Completely Remove IBus Packages (Purge)
bash
코드 복사
sudo apt purge ibus ibus-hangul ibus-gtk ibus-gtk3
Remove remaining dependencies:

bash
코드 복사
sudo apt autoremove --purge
3. Delete User Configuration and Cache (Important)
bash
코드 복사
rm -rf ~/.config/ibus
rm -rf ~/.cache/ibus
rm -rf ~/.local/share/ibus
4. Reset Input Method Environment Configuration
bash
코드 복사
rm -f ~/.xinputrc
5. Clean System Input Method Alternatives (Optional)
bash
코드 복사
sudo update-alternatives --remove-all xinput-all_ALL || true
⚠️ Errors can be safely ignored if no alternatives are configured.

6. Verify IBus Is Fully Removed
Check if the command still exists:

bash
코드 복사
which ibus
Expected output:

text
코드 복사
command not found
Check running processes:

bash
코드 복사
ps aux | grep ibus
→ No running ibus processes should appear.

7. Recommended Replacement: fcitx5
After removing IBus, fcitx5 is strongly recommended for XFCE.

bash
코드 복사
sudo apt install fcitx5 fcitx5-hangul fcitx5-config-qt fcitx5-frontend-gtk3
im-config -n fcitx5
⚠️ Log out and log back in after running the above command.

8. Verify Environment Variables (fcitx5)
bash
코드 복사
echo $GTK_IM_MODULE
echo $QT_IM_MODULE
echo $XMODIFIERS
Expected output:

text
코드 복사
fcitx
fcitx
@im=fcitx
Summary
✔ IBus fully removed

✔ Input method conflicts eliminated

✔ Single input system (fcitx5) configured

✔ Stable Korean/English input on Debian + XFCE

Notes
IBus is primarily optimized for GNOME

fcitx5 works more reliably on XFCE

Running multiple input frameworks simultaneously is not recommended
